      "title": "Create a Vercel KV store",
      "description": "## Create a Vercel KV database\n\n1. Log in to [Vercel](https://vercel.com/), and visit the [Vercel Dashboard](https://vercel.com/dashboard).\n1. Select **Add New** > **Store**.\n1. Select **Create Database**.\n1. Select the **Create** button next to KV.\n1. Name this KV store **test-fga**.\n1. Keep the rest of the options as default.\n1. Select the **Create** button.",
